The paper deals with reinforcement learning (RL) and meta-learning, which are subfields of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on the problem of exploration-exploitation trade-off in RL, which is a common problem in RL and falls under the category of decision making. The paper also introduces a new method for meta-learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
